text:
Hi gura here are some tips and answers for you regarding minecraft:
-jumping on the crops destroys them 

-iron golem farm works by scaring villagers with a zombie. The golem is being spawned on a platform above them and pushed by a water stream into lava blade with hoppers underneath. Each golem drops 3-5 ingots and its output should  be min 60 golems per h. The farm works only if someone is close to it aka if its chunk is loaded... i don`t know what is the render distance set in your server but would guess at least 20chunks(but asking the person that is maintaining the server would be the most precise sollution...if you press F3+G it will show your chunk borders. Same combination to switch it off
if you open a chest and alt tab while the chest is your minecraft does not go into pause mode and this way you can afk while using your computer for other things.  You just switch off the master sound and you are done .
Remember that if nobody is close to the farm it will not work so basically if you are the only one on the server close to the farm you are the one who is producing that iron hence on your place i would do couple afk sessions and just grab all the iron you need. IT IS absulotely essential for you to make sure you are in a safe spot where you cannot be killed during the night( zombies can brake doors), phantoms will attack you if you are not under a roof. I usualy stand on a chest in a corner and wall myself with glass so i can see what is going on outside after i want to stop the afk and go back to the game. Just make sure no mobs can get to you and see you. Also while afk you dont need your gear so put it away just in case you do die.
Don`t afk and build anything just next to the farm though because if an irom golem spawns outside the platform you will have to kill him for the farm to start working properly again.

-F3+H shows you the durability of your items in numbers, F3+B shows you the hitboxes of mobs and things like minecarts and boats just in case you want to make sure you do not hit whatever is that you are trasnporting in your boat or minecart ^^
-The server with the shopping district where everyone has a shop is called HERMICRAFT but there are thousands of their videos so if you want to find anything specific you have to know the crators names and there is a lot of them. and there is 7 seasons of it as well. 
-Piglins attack you if you mine any form of gold open any kind of chest even if you are wearing gold armour, if you want to get something from the chests in piglin stronholds just put a hopper underneath and take the items from the hopper directly.
-Pumbas are afraid of the warped fungus(the green one)... if you place a fungus on a block  they run away 7 or so blocks
so its good to carry one with you for emergencies. also they have a very far reach so they will be able to hit you before you close down on them with a sword.
-you can breed striders with warped fungus, so you should be able to make more of them next to your portal.
-if you can bring a villager somewhere around your area are trap him and put a cauldron next to him he will become a leather worker and on a master lvl trade he sells you saddles for emeralds (make sure to put him in a safe space where mobs cannot get in otherwise you will loose him... use boats to transport him to your are and use minecarts to deliver him where you want him)
